    description: 'FIXED v0.60: data/parsed/chaos_space_marines/armory/general.json "Daemonic flight / jump pack" (Infantry only, p_unit 9 / p_char 19) had desc \'The model gains +6" Movement and the unit type "Jump Pack Infantry"\' but its effect was missing the stat_mod, so the +6" Movement the desc promises was not applied. Added stat_mod: [{ stat: "M", delta: 6 }] to effect, matching the same fix already applied to GK\'s Teleporter.',
